---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuizCard from '../../components/QuizCard.astro';
import Math from '../../components/Math.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 2: 単位系と単位換算">
  <h1>Week 2: 単位系と単位換算</h1>

  <!-- ===== Section 1: 物理世界の基石 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>🌍 なぜ単位を統一する？</h2>
    
    <div class="story-box">
      <div class="story-icon">🚀</div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <strong>1999年、火星探査機が墜落</strong><br/>
        NASAはメートル法、下請け会社はヤード・ポンド法を使用。<br/>
        <span class="highlight-red">単位の違いで1億ドル以上の探査機が失われた！</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 単位の歴史 -->
    <div class="history-grid">
      <div class="history-card">
        <div class="history-header">🇯🇵 尺貫法（〜1958年）</div>
        <div class="history-content">
          <p><strong>一寸</strong> ≈ 3.03 cm　<strong>一尺</strong> ≈ 30.3 cm</p>
          <p><strong>一貫</strong> ≈ 3.75 kg</p>
          <p class="fun-fact">💡 今も使われてる！畳のサイズ、お寿司の「一貫」</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="history-card">
        <div class="history-header">🇬🇧🇺🇸 ヤード・ポンド法</div>
        <div class="history-content">
          <p><strong>1 inch</strong> = 2.54 cm　<strong>1 foot</strong> = 30.48 cm</p>
          <p><strong>1 mile</strong> ≈ 1.6 km　<strong>1 pound</strong> ≈ 454 g</p>
          <p class="fun-fact">💡 アメリカでは今も日常で使用！ゴルフ、野球、身長</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-box">
      <div class="solution-header">💡 解決策：メートル法（SI単位系）</div>
      <div class="solution-content">
        <p>1799年フランスで誕生 → 世界共通の「ものさし」に</p>
        <p><strong>10進法</strong>で計算しやすい！（1 km = 1000 m = 100000 cm）</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 身の回りの単位 -->
    <h3>💡 単位は身の回りにある！</h3>
    <div class="real-world-grid">
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">📱</span>
        <span class="rw-title">スマホの厚さ</span>
        <span class="rw-value">8 mm = 0.008 m</span>
      </div>
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">⚽</span>
        <span class="rw-title">サッカーボール直径</span>
        <span class="rw-value">22 cm = 0.22 m</span>
      </div>
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">✈️</span>
        <span class="rw-title">飛行機の巡航高度</span>
        <span class="rw-value">10 km = 10,000 m</span>
      </div>
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">🔬</span>
        <span class="rw-title">赤血球の直径</span>
        <span class="rw-value">7 μm = 7×10⁻⁶ m</span>
      </div>
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">🧬</span>
        <span class="rw-title">DNAの幅</span>
        <span class="rw-value">2 nm = 2×10⁻⁹ m</span>
      </div>
      <div class="real-world-card">
        <span class="rw-icon">🌊</span>
        <span class="rw-title">マリアナ海溝</span>
        <span class="rw-value">10.9 km = 10,900 m</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>SI基本単位（7つ）</h3>
    <div class="unit-cards-small">
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">m</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">長さ（メートル）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">kg</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">質量（キログラム）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">s</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">時間（秒）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">A</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">電流（アンペア）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">K</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">温度（ケルビン）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">mol</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">物質量（モル）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="unit-card-sm">
        <span class="unit-sym">cd</span>
        <span class="unit-desc">光度（カンデラ）</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="note-text">💡 この授業では主に <strong>m, kg, s</strong> を使います</p>

    <div class="unit-systems">
      <h4>📊 単位系の比較</h4>
      <table class="systems-table">
        <tr>
          <th></th>
          <th>SI (MKS)</th>
          <th>CGS</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>長さ</td>
          <td><strong>m</strong></td>
          <td>cm</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>質量</td>
          <td><strong>kg</strong></td>
          <td>g</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>時間</td>
          <td><strong>s</strong></td>
          <td>s</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>力</td>
          <td><strong>N</strong> (= kg·m/s²)</td>
          <td>dyn (= g·cm/s²)</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p class="note-text">⚠️ 物理では必ず <strong>SI単位</strong> に換算してから計算する！</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 2: 長度単位の階段 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>📐 長さの単位：階段をイメージしよう</h2>
    
    <p class="intro-text">大きい単位は「上」、小さい単位は「下」。<br/>
    <strong>下りる時は ×（大きくなる）、上る時は ÷（小さくなる）</strong></p>

    <!-- 単位階段図 -->
    <div class="unit-ladder">
      <div class="ladder-step step-1">
        <span class="step-unit">km</span>
        <span class="step-value">キロメートル</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ladder-arrow down">×10³</div>
      
      <div class="ladder-step step-2">
        <span class="step-unit">m</span>
        <span class="step-value">メートル（基準）</span>
        <span class="si-badge">SI</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ladder-arrow down">×10²</div>
      
      <div class="ladder-step step-3">
        <span class="step-unit">cm</span>
        <span class="step-value">センチメートル</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ladder-arrow down">×10</div>
      
      <div class="ladder-step step-4">
        <span class="step-unit">mm</span>
        <span class="step-value">ミリメートル</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ladder-arrow down">×10³</div>
      
      <div class="ladder-step step-5">
        <span class="step-unit">μm</span>
        <span class="step-value">マイクロメートル</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ladder-arrow down">×10³</div>
      
      <div class="ladder-step step-6">
        <span class="step-unit">nm</span>
        <span class="step-value">ナノメートル</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prefix-table">
      <h4>📋 接頭語まとめ</h4>
      <table>
        <tr><th>接頭語</th><th>記号</th><th>意味</th><th>例</th></tr>
        <tr><td>キロ</td><td>k</td><td>×10³ (1000倍)</td><td>1 km = 1000 m</td></tr>
        <tr><td>センチ</td><td>c</td><td>×10⁻² (1/100)</td><td>1 cm = 0.01 m</td></tr>
        <tr><td>ミリ</td><td>m</td><td>×10⁻³ (1/1000)</td><td>1 mm = 0.001 m</td></tr>
        <tr><td>マイクロ</td><td>μ</td><td>×10⁻⁶</td><td>1 μm = 0.000001 m</td></tr>
        <tr><td>ナノ</td><td>n</td><td>×10⁻⁹</td><td>1 nm = 10⁻⁹ m</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <strong>⚠️ 注意！</strong> μ（マイクロ）と m（ミリ）を間違える人が多い！<br/>
      1000倍も違います！
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 3: 練習 Level 1 - 基礎 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 1：基礎換算</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">接頭語を数字に置き換えて計算しよう</p>

    <div class="notation-box">
      <strong>📐 解答の書き方</strong>
      <p>物理では<strong>科学記数法（指数表記）</strong>を使います：</p>
      <div class="notation-examples">
        <span class="good">✅ 1.0 × 10³</span>
        <span class="good">✅ 5.0 × 10⁻⁵</span>
        <span class="ok">△ 1000（大きすぎ/小さすぎる数は避ける）</span>
      </div>
      <p class="notation-note">有効数字も意識！ 1.0 と 1 は精度が違う</p>
    </div>

    <QuizCard 
      id="1"
      question="3.5 km"
      answer="3500"
      answerUnit="m"
      steps={[
        "k（キロ）= 10³ = 1000",
        "3.5 km = 3.5 × 1000 m",
        "= <strong>3500 m</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="2"
      question="45 cm"
      answer="0.45"
      answerUnit="m"
      steps={[
        "c（センチ）= 10⁻² = 0.01",
        "45 cm = 45 × 0.01 m",
        "= <strong>0.45 m</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="3"
      question="250 mm"
      answer="0.25"
      answerUnit="m"
      steps={[
        "m（ミリ）= 10⁻³ = 0.001",
        "250 mm = 250 × 0.001 m",
        "= <strong>0.25 m</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="4"
      question="50 μm"
      answer="5 × 10⁻⁵"
      answerUnit="m"
      steps={[
        "μ（マイクロ）= 10⁻⁶",
        "50 μm = 50 × 10⁻⁶ m",
        "= 5 × 10¹ × 10⁻⁶ m",
        "= <strong>5 × 10⁻⁵ m</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="5"
      question="200 mg"
      answer="2 × 10⁻⁴"
      answerUnit="kg"
      steps={[
        "mg → kg は2ステップ！",
        "① mg → g: 200 mg = 0.2 g",
        "② g → kg: 0.2 g = 0.2 × 10⁻³ kg",
        "= <strong>2 × 10⁻⁴ kg</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="mgからkgは「m(10⁻³)」を2回かける = 10⁻⁶"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 3.5: 跨階換算 + 逆向換算 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 1.5：接頭語どうしの換算</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">基準単位を経由せず、接頭語間で直接変換！</p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>💡 ポイント</strong>
      <p>μm → nm のような「微小単位どうし」の変換では、指数の差を計算する：</p>
      <p>μ = 10⁻⁶、n = 10⁻⁹ → 差は 10³（1000倍）</p>
    </div>

    <QuizCard 
      id="5.1"
      question="1.0 m"
      answer="1.0 × 10³"
      answerUnit="mm"
      steps={[
        "m → mm は「大→小」なので数字が大きくなる",
        "1 m = 1000 mm = 10³ mm",
        "= <strong>1.0 × 10³ mm</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="下りる時は ×（大きくなる）"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="5.2"
      question="1.0 × 10⁻¹ μm"
      answer="1.0 × 10²"
      answerUnit="nm"
      steps={[
        "μ = 10⁻⁶、n = 10⁻⁹",
        "μm → nm は ×10³（1000倍大きくなる）",
        "1.0 × 10⁻¹ × 10³ = 1.0 × 10⁻¹⁺³",
        "= <strong>1.0 × 10² nm</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="μ(10⁻⁶) から n(10⁻⁹) へは ×10³"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="5.3"
      question="500 nm"
      answer="0.5"
      answerUnit="μm"
      steps={[
        "nm → μm は「小→大」なので数字が小さくなる",
        "n = 10⁻⁹、μ = 10⁻⁶ → 差は 10⁻³（÷1000）",
        "500 × 10⁻³ = 0.5 μm",
        "= <strong>0.5 μm</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="5.4"
      question="2.5 kg"
      answer="2.5 × 10⁶"
      answerUnit="mg"
      steps={[
        "kg → g: ×10³",
        "g → mg: ×10³",
        "合計: ×10⁶",
        "2.5 × 10⁶ = <strong>2,500,000 mg</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="kg → mg は2段階下りる = ×10⁶"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 4: 面積・体積（重点！） ===== -->
  <section class="content-section danger-zone">
    <h2>⚠️ 超重要！面積と体積の換算</h2>
    
    <div class="danger-banner">
      <span class="danger-icon">🚨</span>
      <span>ここで多くの人が間違える！</span>
    </div>

    <div class="key-question">
      <p>問題：<strong>1 m = 100 cm</strong> なら、<strong>1 m² = 100 cm²</strong> ？</p>
      <p class="answer-reveal">❌ <strong>違います！</strong> 1 m² = <span class="big-num">10000</span> cm²</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 面積比較図 -->
    <div class="area-comparison">
      <div class="comparison-side">
        <h4>長さ（1次元）</h4>
        <div class="line-demo">
          <div class="line-full">1 m</div>
          <div class="line-small">1 cm</div>
        </div>
        <p>1 cm = 10⁻² m<br/><span class="note">（100等分の1つ）</span></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="comparison-side">
        <h4>面積（2次元）</h4>
        <div class="grid-demo">
          <div class="grid-container">
            <div class="grid-highlight"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-label">100 × 100 = 10000個</div>
        </div>
        <p>1 cm² = (10⁻²)² = <strong>10⁻⁴</strong> m²<br/><span class="note">（10000等分の1つ）</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="formula-box">
      <h4>🔑 黄金ルール</h4>
      <div class="formula">
        <p><strong>面積</strong>：指数を <span class="highlight-orange">2倍</span> にする</p>
        <p class="example">cm → m は ×10⁻² → cm² → m² は ×10⁻⁴</p>
      </div>
      <div class="formula">
        <p><strong>体積</strong>：指数を <span class="highlight-orange">3倍</span> にする</p>
        <p class="example">cm → m は ×10⁻² → cm³ → m³ は ×10⁻⁶</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 5: 練習 Level 2 - 面積 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 2：面積換算</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">指数を2倍にすることを忘れずに！</p>

    <QuizCard 
      id="6"
      question="300 cm²"
      answer="0.03"
      answerUnit="m²"
      steps={[
        "長さ：1 cm = 10⁻² m",
        "面積：1 cm² = (10⁻²)² = 10⁻⁴ m²",
        "300 cm² = 300 × 10⁻⁴ m²",
        "= <strong>0.03 m²</strong> (= 3 × 10⁻² m²)"
      ]}
      hint="cm² → m² は ÷10000！（÷100 ではない！）"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="7"
      question="50 mm²"
      answer="5 × 10⁻⁵"
      answerUnit="m²"
      steps={[
        "長さ：1 mm = 10⁻³ m",
        "面積：1 mm² = (10⁻³)² = 10⁻⁶ m²",
        "50 mm² = 50 × 10⁻⁶ m²",
        "= <strong>5 × 10⁻⁵ m²</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="8"
      question="2.5 km²"
      answer="2.5 × 10⁶"
      answerUnit="m²"
      steps={[
        "長さ：1 km = 10³ m",
        "面積：1 km² = (10³)² = 10⁶ m²",
        "2.5 km² = 2.5 × 10⁶ m²",
        "= <strong>2,500,000 m²</strong>"
      ]}
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 6: 練習 Level 3 - 体積 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 3：体積換算</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">指数を3倍に！また、1 L = 1 dm³ = 10⁻³ m³</p>

    <QuizCard 
      id="9"
      question="4000 cm³"
      answer="4 × 10⁻³"
      answerUnit="m³"
      steps={[
        "長さ：1 cm = 10⁻² m",
        "体積：1 cm³ = (10⁻²)³ = 10⁻⁶ m³",
        "4000 cm³ = 4000 × 10⁻⁶ m³",
        "= 4 × 10³ × 10⁻⁶ m³",
        "= <strong>4 × 10⁻³ m³</strong> = 0.004 m³"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="10"
      question="2.5 L"
      answer="2.5 × 10⁻³"
      answerUnit="m³"
      steps={[
        "1 L = 1 dm³（立方デシメートル）",
        "1 dm = 10⁻¹ m",
        "1 L = 1 dm³ = (10⁻¹)³ = 10⁻³ m³",
        "2.5 L = <strong>2.5 × 10⁻³ m³</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="覚えよう：1 L = 10⁻³ m³ = 0.001 m³"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="11"
      question="500 mL"
      answer="5 × 10⁻⁴"
      answerUnit="m³"
      steps={[
        "mL → L：500 mL = 0.5 L",
        "L → m³：1 L = 10⁻³ m³",
        "0.5 L = 0.5 × 10⁻³ m³",
        "= <strong>5 × 10⁻⁴ m³</strong>"
      ]}
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 7: 複合単位 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>🔀 複合単位の換算</h2>
    <p class="intro-text">分数の形で考える：<strong>分子と分母を別々に換算</strong>してから計算</p>

    <!-- 複合単位のフロー図 -->
    <div class="compound-flow">
      <div class="flow-example">
        <div class="flow-title">例：g/cm³ → kg/m³</div>
        <div class="flow-diagram">
          <div class="flow-fraction">
            <div class="flow-num">
              <span class="label">分子（質量）</span>
              <span class="calc">1 g → 10⁻³ kg</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
            <div class="flow-den">
              <span class="label">分母（体積）</span>
              <span class="calc">1 cm³ → 10⁻⁶ m³</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-result">
            <span class="calc-final">10⁻³ ÷ 10⁻⁶</span>
            <span class="calc-final">= 10⁻³⁺⁶ = <strong>10³</strong></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-conclusion">
          ∴ 1 g/cm³ = <strong>1000 kg/m³</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-box">
      <strong>💡 覚えておくと便利</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>km/h → m/s：<strong>÷ 3.6</strong></li>
        <li>g/cm³ → kg/m³：<strong>× 1000</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Section 8: 練習 Level 4 - 複合単位 ===== -->
  <section class="content-section exercise-section">
    <h2>✏️ 練習 Level 4：複合単位</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">分子・分母を分けて考えよう</p>

    <QuizCard 
      id="12"
      question="72 km/h"
      answer="20"
      answerUnit="m/s"
      steps={[
        "分数で書く：72 km / 1 h",
        "分子：72 km = 72 × 1000 m = 72000 m",
        "分母：1 h = 3600 s",
        "72000 m ÷ 3600 s = <strong>20 m/s</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="速攻法：km/h → m/s は ÷ 3.6 (72 ÷ 3.6 = 20)"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="13"
      question="2.5 g/cm³"
      answer="2500"
      answerUnit="kg/m³"
      steps={[
        "分子：2.5 g = 2.5 × 10⁻³ kg",
        "分母：1 cm³ = 10⁻⁶ m³",
        "(2.5 × 10⁻³) ÷ (10⁻⁶)",
        "= 2.5 × 10⁻³⁺⁶ = 2.5 × 10³",
        "= <strong>2500 kg/m³</strong>"
      ]}
      hint="g/cm³ の数字に 1000 をかけると kg/m³"
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="14"
      question="13.6 g/cm³（水銀の密度）"
      answer="13600"
      answerUnit="kg/m³"
      steps={[
        "g/cm³ → kg/m³ は × 1000",
        "13.6 × 1000 = <strong>13600 kg/m³</strong>"
      ]}
    />

    <QuizCard 
      id="14.1"
      question="1.0 × 10³ kg/m³（水の密度）"
      answer="1.0"
      answerUnit="g/cm³"
      steps={[
        "kg/m³ → g/cm³ は逆方向！",
        "kg → g: ×10³",
